descriptionNullable:
The images used in this dataset are collected from [Laboro Tomato](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/nexuswho/laboro-tomato)
This Dataset offers a collection of images tailored for CNN models, DL, and ML applications. It features meticulously sorted images of tomatoes categorized into ripe and unripe stages, with separate training and testing sets for model evaluation. 

Each image is labelled accordingly, supporting tasks like classification, detection, and segmentation. 

- Example of ripe tomatoes 

![ripe](https://www.googleapis.com/download/storage/v1/b/kaggle-user-content/o/inbox%2F11887723%2F014349530630fc7f3c09426d38f4dc45%2Fimagy-image(1).jpg?generation=1708266930133459&alt=media)
